<h2>Your BMI</h2>
<div class="result"><div class="r1"><br />?</div></div>
<h2>BMI Categories:</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Underweight</strong> below 18.5</li>
<li><strong>Normal weight</strong> between 18.5 and 24.9</li>
<li><strong>Overweight</strong> between 25 and 29.9</li>
<li><strong>Obesity</strong> more or greater than 30</li>
</ul>
</td>
<td valign="top" style="width:280px;">
<h2>How to calculate BMI?</h2>
<p>Calculate your Body Mass Index (with this friendly BMI calculator) and compare
yourself to other women or men of the same weight and height.
</p>
<ol>
<li>Enter your weight and height using American or Metric measures.</li>
<li>Click on <em>Calculate BMI</em>.</li>
<li>Check your BMI in the middle.</li>
</ol>
